Trade/Device Name(s): One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test
One Step HCG Serum/Urine Combo Pregnancy Test
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for One Step HCG Pregnancy Tests (Urine and Serum/Urine Combo) using immunoassay for qualitative detection of hCG.
Indications for Use Summary: For qualitative determination of hCG in human urine (all formats) and serum (combo format) to aid early pregnancy detection; midstream format OTC, other formats OTC and professional use.
